            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報26200點，升243點，較上日現貨收市價25967點高水232點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報6045點，升85點，高水94點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報9374點，升79點，高水73點。</p>\n</div>",
